1. You can control the player by 'Up' and 'Down' arrows, you shoot by pressing 'space' button.
2. There is 9 different types of enemies you can shoot, they have diferent points and damage values.
3. You can get power ups by shooting or collapsing some special enemies (they are glowing).
4. You have 30 seconds to play and to win you need at least 80 points.
5. There is sound affects and animations, they suppose to work in harmony.
6. I checked for Chrome and works fine, please let me know if there is any trouble if you try any other browser!